'''詹姆斯·「吉姆」·赫奇斯'''（{{lang-en|James "Jim" Hedges}}；{{bd|1938年|5月10日|}}），是一名美國[[禁酒令|禁酒]]活動家及前[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]][[富爾頓縣_(賓夕法尼亞州)|富爾頓縣]]{{le|湯普森鎮 (賓夕法尼亞州)|Thompson Township, Fulton County, Pennsylvania|湯普森鎮}}的{{le|評稅|Tax assessment|估稅員}}，也是自1959年以來及二十一世紀唯一一名曾出任公職的[[禁酒黨|禁酒黨]]黨員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ballot-access.org/2001/1201.html|title=Many Minor Parties Win Elections|date=December 1, 2001|work=[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]]|publisher=[[Richard_Winger|Richard Winger]]|accessdate=1 June 2011|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304024135/http://www.ballot-access.org/2001/1201.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
赫奇斯參與了[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]，最初是尋求禁酒黨的總統候選人提名的主席格雷格·塞爾策（Greg Seltzer）之{{le|競選搭檔|Running mate}}。2015年4月，塞爾策因{{le|馬里蘭州州長|Governor of Maryland}}[[拉里·霍甘|拉里·霍甘]]提名為馬里蘭州選舉委員會委員而撤回提名及辭去黨主席職務；赫奇斯就此成為禁酒黨總統候選人<ref name="resigns">{{cite web | url=http://www.independentpoliticalreport.com/2015/04/greg-seltzer-resigns-as-prohibition-party-chairman/ | title=Greg Seltzer Resigns as Prohibition Party Chairman | work=Independent Political Report | date=April 22, 2015 | accessdate=August 3, 2015 | archive-date=2020-09-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919193613/https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2015/04/greg-seltzer-resigns-as-prohibition-party-chairman/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.tampabay.com/news/politics/stateroundup/too-many-presidential-candidates-what-about-the-anarchist-socialist/2237130 | title=Too many presidential candidates? What about the anarchist, socialist, prohibitionist — and cat | work=[[Tampa_Bay_Times|Tampa Bay Times]] | date=July 13, 2015 | accessdate=August 3, 2015 | author=Garvin, Glenn | archive-date=2021-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122023034/https://www.tampabay.com/news/politics/stateroundup/too-many-presidential-candidates-what-about-the-anarchist-socialist/2237130/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他在2015年7月31日舉行的禁酒黨全國代表大會電話會議中正式提名為2016年總統候選人，競選搭檔為密西西比州的比爾·貝葉斯（Bill Bayes）<ref name="nominates">{{cite web|url=http://ballot-access.org/2015/07/31/prohibition-party-nominates-national-ticket/|title=Prohibition Party Nominates National Ticket|date=August 1, 2015|work=Ballot Access News|publisher=Richard Winger|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2015-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803043129/http://ballot-access.org/2015/07/31/prohibition-party-nominates-national-ticket/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，又參與了美國獨立黨主在加利福尼亞州的初選，獲得10.8%選票和[[萊克縣_(加利福尼亞州)|萊克縣]]的代表提名<ref>"Prohibitionist Runs Strong in California" American Third Party Report. June 9th, 2016. Accessed August 6th, 2016. {{cite web |url=https://amthirdpartyreport.com/2016/06/09/prohibitionist-runs-strong-in-california/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-08-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611000056/https://amthirdpartyreport.com/2016/06/09/prohibitionist-runs-strong-in-california/ |archivedate=2016-06-11 }}</ref>。

